Jaipur was founded by Maharaja Sawai Jai Singh on 18th November 1727
Also known as the Pink City, it is the capital of Rajasthan.
Jaipur is touted as the first planned city of India.
It is spread in a wide area of 11,117.8 sq. kilometres.
Jaipur is a major tourist spot containing historically significant Hawa Mahal, Amber Fort, City Palace, etc.
The city is also famous for its handicrafts, jewellery, fabrics and carpets.


